OL,5, A US billionaire has been banned for   
OL,6, life from buying antiquities after an  
OL,7, investigation found that items he owned
OL,8, had been looted and illegally smuggled.
OL,10,FMichael Steinhardt has surrendered     
OL,11,Ftreasures worth $70m (#53m) as part of 
OL,12,Fa deal which means he will not face    
OL,13,Fcriminal charges.                      
OL,15,FThe ban on the hedge-fund pioneer      
OL,16,Facquiring more antiquities was the     
OL,17,Ffirst of its kind, prosecutors said.   
OL,19,FMany of the antiquities appeared to be 
OL,20,Fwithout provenance, they said.         
